{"about_the_game":"Ever wondered what happens after you\u2026well, don\u2019t? In COLD TRAIL you play as a ghost investigating his own death. This beautiful world, flitting through vibrant landscapes and poetic settings hides a dark secret: your own demise.<br><br>COLD TRAIL is an adventure game focused on exploration, collecting clues, solving mysteries and puzzles. Featuring quirky characters to meet and many surprise to discover in a handpainted world. <br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217040/extras/ExploreTheWorldText.png?t=1725992481\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217040/extras/ExploreTheWorldPlain.gif?t=1725992481\" /><br><br>From the heart of the village to the deepest woods, a converted farm turned fortune-telling kiosk and a trailer park turned post-apocalytic bunker, every corner invites observation and exploration.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217040/extras/UnlockSkillsText.png?t=1725992481\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217040/extras/UnlockSkillsPlain.gif?t=1725992481\" /><br><br>You start the story as an amateur ghost, unfamiliar with the job. As the adventure progresses, you will master the role of a ghost and unlock ghostly abilities.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217040/extras/MeetCharactersText.png?t=1725992481\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217040/extras/MeetCharactersPlain.gif?t=1725992481\" /><br><br>In this setting, where houses are spaced out, personalities have more room to develop. Memorable characters will cross your path. <br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/st